{"tid":1258933,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無兔友telegram 群？","createTime":"2019-06-26T10:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T11:49:38.000Z","uid":269791,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2699c5cdb93c6c5724ea9b575e85bcc2fdfac57a","tid":1258933,"uid":269791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"想知道有無專系分享兔仔資訊嘅群組。<br />\n大概可能系一班養開兔仔嘅主人會系裏面分享咩獸醫好啊、照顧病左嘅兔仔需要主意嘅事項啊 又或者係兔仔中意挽咩 等等嘅群？<br />\n最近屋企隻兔仔受傷整親自已，之後我系網上又或者系高登呢到不停咁刨唔同嘅post 同文章，然後我就系到諗「如果可以有一個群可以集合到有關兔仔嘅資訊同主人就好啦，因為可有咩嘅問題都可以有其他人嘅經驗話比你聽」。<br />\n所以系呢到，想問下咁多位絲打巴打你哋知唔知有無嘅咁嘅群？<br />\n如果真系無，我好唔好開個？<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee7fbd6a660581217864c9f527f219d73fef060","tid":1258933,"uid":260312,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:53:44.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"520b30066a1b6624fdd7bb7741218e82fcd2d399","tid":1258933,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:54:23.000Z","msg":"吾系"},{"pid":"0d115886c4688312f60ecffa44b2872fe83ce25e","tid":1258933,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"開個吧"},{"pid":"2fbe09df8ee1930774e241744b43f179e0cac108","tid":1258933,"uid":269791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d115886c4688312f60ecffa44b2872fe83ce25e","tid":1258933,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"開個吧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯，但要點樣令多啲人知道？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c655dd32e8d7c397917d939f4141774157b799a","tid":1258933,"uid":130586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fbe09df8ee1930774e241744b43f179e0cac108","tid":1258933,"uid":269791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid